# ErrorMonitoring.intent , MVP Customer Portal / Deployment Readiness

mission ErrorMonitoring

goal
  Capture and report application errors for operators.

why
  Unmonitored errors mean outages are discovered by customers, not the team. But
  error payloads are a common place secrets and PII leak.

input
  error: ApplicationError

output
  report: ErrorReport

guarantees
  errors are captured and reported
  error reports are scrubbed of secrets and PII

guarantee error reports are scrubbed of secrets and PII
  because stack traces and payloads routinely carry tokens and personal data
  verify test secrets are scrubbed from reports

never
  log(secret)
  include PII in an error report

verify
  test secrets are scrubbed from reports
